We are excited to announce that we are in the final stages of upgrading the Powe...
We are excited to announce that we are in the final stages of upgrading the PowerGUI community to our new platform. With that upgrade will come a better, faster, and more organized site. In these final stages we will have to lock down the current site until April 6th 2014. As of March 27, you will not be able to post any new threads or reply to existing threads. The forums will be available once again on the Dell TechCenter community on April 6, the day when we launch the community on the new platform. The PowerGUI community will become a part of the Dell Tech Center community located at http://en.community.dell.com/techcenter . You can expect to receive an email with your user account credentials, along with instructions on how to set up your account in the next few weeks until then, feel free to browse the other software communities today. We apologize for any inconvenience this causes but believe the new site will benefit everyone when it is up and running. TechCenter - Dell Community en.community.dell.com
